    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Nageia excelsa are fever and cough, primarily due to its antibacterial properties, which inhibit the growth of pathogens responsible for these conditions. Additionally, Nageia excelsa has been used to treat hypertension as it contains flavonoids that help regulate blood pressure. Its anti-inflammatory properties also make it effective in reducing swelling and pain associated with arthritis, a chronic condition characterized by joint inflammation. Furthermore, the plant's antiviral properties aid in the recovery from viral infections such as herpes, which causes skin lesions and sores. Moreover, Nageia excelsa has been utilized to alleviate diarrhea, a symptom of gastrointestinal infections caused by bacteria or viruses.",
